"ເລັ່ງການ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຈັດຊື້</font></strong> ຂອງທ່ານ. ຕິດຕ"
"າມສາງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ, ແລະ ຕິດຕາມການຈັດສົ່ງຂອງທ່ານໃນ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-"
"1\">ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ</font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Finally, use the <b>Allocation</b> button to assign the MO to the <b>Sales "
"Order</b>."
msgstr ""
"ສຸດທ້າຍ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <b>ການຈັດສັນ</b> ເພື່ອມອບໝາຍ MO ໃຫ້ກັບ <b>ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ</b>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Follow your equipment status and maintenance with the <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Maintenance App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຕິດຕາມສະຖານະອຸປະກອນ ແລະ ການບຳລຸງຮັກສາຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ແອັບການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ</font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Follow your planning and keep track of worked time in the <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning &amp; Timesheets Apps</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຕິດຕາມການວາງແຜນ ແລະ ບັນທຶກເວລາເຮັດວຽກໃນແອັບ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-"
"1\">ການວາງແຜນ &amp; ໃບບັນທຶກເວລາ</font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For this use case, open the David Patel quotation. You can see a complete "
"setup using all the products mentioned in the previous topic."
msgstr ""
"ສຳລັບກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້ນີ້, ໃຫ້ເປີດໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງ David Patel. ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນການຕັ້ງຄ່າທີ່ສົມບູນໂດຍໃ"
"ຊ້ສິນຄ້າທັງໝົດທີ່ໄດ້ກ່າວມາໃນຫົວຂໍ້ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "From the David Patel quotation, we placed"
msgstr "ຈາກໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງ David Patel, ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ວາງ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:sale.order.template.line,name:custom_furniture.sale_order_template_line_3
msgid "Furnitures"
msgstr "ເເຟີນີເຈີ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/custom_furniture/static/src/js/my_tour.js:0
msgid "Get on track and explore our recommendations for your Odoo usage here!"
msgstr ""
"ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ສຳຫຼວດຄຳແນະນຳຂອງພວກເຮົາສຳລັບການນຳໃຊ້ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ນີ້!"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to the Shop Floor App and validate the first step of your production by "
"clicking on it. Continue with the other steps until you can register your "
"production."
msgstr ""
"ໄປທີ່ແອັບ Shop Floor ແລະ ຢືນຢັນຂັ້ນຕອນທຳອິດຂອງການຜະລິດຂອງທ່ານໂດຍການຄລິກໃສ່ມັນ. ດຳເນີນການຂັ້ນຕ"
"ອນອື່ນໆຕໍ່ໄປຈົນກວ່າທ່ານຈະສາມາດລົງທະບຽນການຜະລິດຂອງທ່ານໄດ້."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "ສະບາຍດີ!"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you do not have a specific installation task or want to deliver it "
"separately, you can do it in the Inventory App."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານບໍ່ມີວຽກຕິດຕັ້ງສະເພາະ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການຈັດສົ່ງແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ, ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ໃນແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you usually structure your quotations similarly, use the Quotation "
"Template feature. It will allow you to configure a set of products and "
"sections that will always be imported when you select it."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານປົກກະຕິຈັດໂຄງສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານຄ້າຍຄືກັນ, ໃຫ້ໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດແບບຢ່າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ. ມັນຈະຊ່ວຍ"
"ໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດຄ່າຊຸດສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ໝວດໝູ່ທີ່ຈະຖືກນຳເຂົ້າມາສະເໝີເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກມັນ."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Demo - Use Case. (In the next Knowledge "
"Article)"
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການປະຕິບັດການທັດສະນະແນະນຳຂອງໂມດູນນີ້, ທ່ານຄວນນຳເຂົ້າມາຂໍ້ມູນສາທິດ ແລະ ລອງໃຊ້ "
"Demo - Use Case. (ໃນບົດຄວາມຄວາມຮູ້ຕໍ່ໄປ)"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to remove this part of your process, you can use reordering "
"rules. These will ensure a fluid replenishment based on minimum quantities "
"of each product or based on orders."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການລຶບສ່ວນນີ້ຂອງຂັ້ນຕອນຂອງທ່ານອອກ, ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ກົດການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນ. ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຮັບປະກັນການເຕີມສິ"
"ນຄ້າທີ່ຄ່ອງຕົວໂດຍອີງຕາມຈຳນວນຕ່ຳສຸດຂອງແຕ່ລະສິນຄ້າ ຫຼື ອີງຕາມຄຳສັ່ງຊື້."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In <b>version 19.1</b>, this field uses <b>HTML</b>, making it easy to share"
" crucial context, including uploading <b>images</b>, adding "
"<b>documents</b>, or <b>linking</b> to relevant articles in the Knowledge "
"app."
msgstr ""
"ໃນ <b>ເວີຊັນ 19.1</b>, ຟິນນີ້ໃຊ້ <b>HTML</b>, ເຮັດໃຫ້ງ່າຍຕໍ່ການແບ່ງປັນເນື້ອຫາທີ່ສຳຄັນ, ລວມທັງການ"
"ອັບໂຫຼດ <b>ຮູບພາບ</b>, ການເພີ່ມ <b>ເອກະສານ</b>, ຫຼື <b>ການເຊື່ອມໂຍງ</b> ໄປຫາບົດຄວາມທີ່ກ່ຽວ"
"ຂ້ອງໃນແອັບຄວາມຮູ້."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:project.task.type,name:custom_furniture.project_task_type_19
msgid "In progress"
msgstr "ກຳລັງດຳເນີນການ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the Purchase Apps, you can see all your Requests For Quotation, which are"
" ready to be sent to your providers. When you have confirmation that your "
"order has been placed, confirm each RFQ to continue the process."
msgstr ""
"ໃນແອັບການຈັດຊື້, ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໃບຮ້ອງຂໍໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານ, ເຊິ່ງພ້ອມທີ່ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອ"
"ງທ່ານ. ເມື່ອທ່ານມີການຢືນຢັນວ່າຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກວາງແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ຢືນຢັນແຕ່ລະ RFQ ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່"
"ໄປ."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In this App, you can see that the delivery is not yet ready to be shipped, as you currently don't have the necessary products. If you navigate to Operations &gt; Replenishment, you will find the list of suggested purchase/manufacture\n"
"        orders missing to complete this order. Select everything, and click on \"Replenish\" &gt; \"Order.\""
msgstr ""
"ໃນແອັບນີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າການຈັດສົ່ງຍັງບໍ່ພ້ອມທີ່ຈະຖືກສົ່ງອອກ, ເນື່ອງຈາກປະຈຸບັນທ່ານບໍ່ມີສິນຄ້າທີ່ຈຳເປັນ. "
"ຖ້າທ່ານໄປທີ່ ການດຳເນີນງານ &gt; ການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ, ທ່ານຈະພົບລາຍການໃບສັ່ງຊື້/ການຜະລິດທີ່ແນະນຳທີ່ຍັງຂາດຢູ່"
"ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ນີ້ສົມບູນ. ເລືອກທັງໝົດ, ແລະ ຄລິກໃສ່ \"ເຕີມສິນຄ້າ\" &gt; \"ສັ່ງຊື້.\""

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.template,name:custom_furniture.product_product_2_product_template
msgid "Initial design consultation and space assessment"
msgstr "ການປຶກສາຫາລືການອອກແບບເບື້ອງຕົ້ນ ແລະ ການປະເມີນສະຖານທີ່"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:sale.order.template.line,name:custom_furniture.sale_order_template_line_5
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "ການຕິດຕັ້ງ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:planning.role,name:custom_furniture.planning_role_1
msgid "Installer"
msgstr "ຜູ້ຕິດຕັ້ງ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "ສາງສິນຄ້າ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:custom_furniture.product_attribute_value_6
msgid "Invisible"
msgstr "ບໍ່ໃຫ້ເຫັນ"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Invoice at the right time with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Invoice App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ໃນເວລາທີ່ເໝາະສົມດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</"
"font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Level up your Manufacture process with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Manufacturing App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຍົກລະດັບຂັ້ນຕອນການຜະລິດຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການຜະລິ"
"ດ</font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>,\n"
"                <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການທຸກຊ່ອງທາງການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານໃນບ່ອນດຽວກັບ Odoo <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-"
"1\">ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"ການຕະຫຼາດທາງອີເມລ</font></strong>,\n"
"                <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງຄົມ</"
"font></strong>, ແລະ <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດທາງ SMS</"
"font></strong>."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ງ່າຍກວ່າທີ່ເຄີຍດ້ວຍສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນຢ່າງສົມບູນ. (<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບການບັນຊີ</font></strong>)"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your employees and all your human resources using the <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">HR Suite.</font></strong>"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການພະນັກງານຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ຊັບພະຍາກອນມະນຸດທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານໂດຍໃຊ້ <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຊຸດ HR.</font></strong>"

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your entire projects with the Project App. You can see that your Sale"
" Order has created a Project with a bunch of already configured tasks. "
"Follow the evolution of your project with tasks, stages, status, and "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການໂຄງການທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍແອັບໂຄງການ. ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າໃບສັ່ງຂາຍຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ສ້າງໂຄງການທີ່ມີວ"
"ຽກທີ່ຖືກກຳນົດຄ່າໄວ້ແລ້ວ. ຕິດຕາມວິວັດທະນາການຂອງໂຄງການຂອງທ່ານດ້ວຍວຽກ, ຂັ້ນຕອນ, ສະຖານະ, ແລະ ກິດ"
"ຈະກຳຕ່າງໆ."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Managing your products and their characteristics is critical in Odoo. This "
"package includes several configs, which you can explore by navigating to the"
" Sales App -&gt; Products."
msgstr ""
"ການຈັດການສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ຄຸນລັກສະນະຂອງມັນແມ່ນສິ່ງສຳຄັນໃນ Odoo. ແພັກເກດນີ້ລວມມີການກຳນົດຄ່າຫຼາຍຢ່າງ, ເ"
"ຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດສຳຫຼວດໄດ້ໂດຍການໄປທີ່ແອັບການຂາຍ -&gt; ສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: custom_furniture
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:custom_furniture.welcome_article_body
